  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: cff4d1da61d2a064cb0712eaa79b5ca5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  TutorialText:
  - To begin, use [left click] to use your KATANA to cut straight through the marble.
    Your goal is to CUT AROUND the BLUE TARGET
  - Now hold [right click] to angle the sword to cut off the marble at the top.
  - When you've finished sculpting the current target, press [enter] to continue
    to the next sculpture in the level
  - Each level has three targets with increasing difficulty. This target requires
    you to rotate the marble with [Q & E] to sculpt successfully
  - 'Now that Bill has given you the TANTO, you can now make more precise cuts. Equip
    it by pressing [2]'
  - Hold [left click] and drag to cut with the TANTO.
  - Cut into previous cuts from a different angle to cut off large pieces of  marble
  - You can always re-equip your KATANA by pressing [1].
  - If you cut too deep into the marble, pressing [H] to change target visibility
    might help - but if it's a lost cause you can always press [R] to restart the
    sculpture
  DialogueBox: {fileID: 2042925753}
  LetterSpeed: 0.01
  DoTutorial: 0
